(11, 1, '2011-09-19 23:48:54', '2011-09-19 23:48:54', '[lulacruza-icon name="shell"]\r\n<div class="small-title">ESPERANDO\r\n<span class="italic">el</span> TSUNAMI</div>\r\n<div class="divider-top-sm"></div>\r\n<p style="font-size: 22px;"><strong>the film</strong></p>\r\n<p style="font-size: 19px;">"An intoxicating picture &amp; sound piece disguised as a road movie"</p>\r\n“Vincent Moon is back with what he calls his best film ever. We are not reluctant to agree\r\nwith him… Lulacruza travel across Colombia to take the country’s musical nectar and\r\ntransform it into their almost shamanic trance sessions, Moon follows closely with his\r\nsensuous-seeking camera and responsive musicianship...\r\n\r\nA magical-realism love story of the most beautiful kind." CPH:DOX\r\n\r\nOfficial Selection for the Sound and Vision Award\r\n<div class="divider-lg"></div>\r\n<ul id="trailer-thumb-container">\r\n	<li class="trailer-thumb" style="background: url(''/esperando/wp-content/themes/esperando/img/teaser_1.gif'');">\r\n<div class="trailer-thumb-content">\r\n<div class="divider-dotted-md"></div>\r\n<p style="margin: 0 auto; font-size: 24px;">teaser</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0 auto; font-size: 90px; line-height: 40px;">one</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="btn-rect btn-rect-sm read-more"><a href="#">play</a></div>\r\n<div class="divider-dotted-md"></div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n	<li class="trailer-thumb" style="background: url(''/esperando/wp-content/themes/esperando/img/teaser_2.gif'');">\r\n<div class="trailer-thumb-content">\r\n<div class="divider-dotted-md"></div>\r\n<p style="margin: 0 auto; font-size: 24px;">teaser</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 0 auto; font-size: 90px; line-height: 40px;">two</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="btn-rect btn-rect-sm read-more"><a href="#">play</a></div>\r\n<div class="divider-dotted-md"></div>\r\n</div></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div id="trailer-container">\r\n<div id="trailers">\r\n<div class="trailer"><span class="heading">teaser one</span>\r\n\r\n\r\n<object width="800" height="45