(239, 3, '2011-11-03 23:03:01', '2011-11-03 23:03:01', '<div class="scrn-col-left">\n<h3>WHAT''S THE DIFFERENCE?</h3>\n<strong>Private-Public Concerts </strong>will begin <strong><em>March 2012</em></strong>. Anyone can host a concert and the rules for Private-Public Concert are very simple. The concerts needs to be public and have a minimum capacity of 25 people.<strong>Private-Public Concerts</strong> can take place in people''s homes, at cafés, in libraries – pretty much anywhere. You can read more about them at <a title="Host a Concert" href="http://localhost:8888/lulacruza/concerts/host-a-concert-description/">Host a Concert</a>.\n\n<strong>Official Concerts</strong> are hosted by venues, cinemas, festivals or other players in the cultural and entertainment world. They can be free, they can have an entrance fee, they can be part of film festivals or concerts.\n<h3></h3>\n<h3>PRIVATE-PUBLIC SCREENINGS</h3>\n<div class="scrn-country-select">[concerts_country_select]</div>\n<div class="scrn-screenings">[concerts]</div>\n</div>\n<div class="scrn-col-right">\n<h3>OFFICIAL CONCERTS</h3>\nFollow us on <a title="Facebook Lulacruza" href="https://www.facebook.com/lulacruza" target="_blank">facebook</a> and <a title="Twitter Lulacruza" href="http://twitter.com/lulacruza" target="_blank">twitter</a> to be updated about new official screenings.\n<div>\n<div>March</div>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n<div>10.02 - Basel, CH / 1.Stock / free entrance</div></li>\n	<li>\n<div>10.02 - Basel, CH / 1.Stock / free entrance</div></li>\n	<li>\n<div>10.02 - Basel, CH / 1.Stock / free entrance</div></li>\n	<li>\n<div>10.02 - Basel, CH / 1.Stock / free entrance</div></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div>\n<div>April</div>\n<ul>\n	<li>\n<div>10.02 - Basel, CH / 1.Stock / free entrance</div></li>\n	<li>\n<div>10.02 - Basel, CH / 1.Stock / free entrance</div></li>\n	<li>\n<div>10.02 - Basel, CH / 1.Stock / free entrance</div></li>\n	<li>\n<div>10.02 - Basel, CH / 1.Stock / free entrance</div></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n&nb