(258, 5, '2011-11-03 22:45:05', '2011-11-03 22:45:05', '[lulacruza-icon name="ship"]\r\n\r\n<div class="small-title">ESPERANDO<br><span class="italic">el</span> TSUNAMI</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="divider-top-sm">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<p style="font-size:22px;">outtakes</p>\r\n\r\n<p>During our travels, we encountered some amazing musicians. In the next few months \r\nwe will be uploading their films and mini-albums periodically. \r\n\r\nExpect music from: Aterciopelados, Cantadoras de Guapi, Chirimia del Rio Napi, \r\nAgusa & The Original, Grupo Guascanato, Pampei, Paito Sixto Salgado, Jorge Henriquez, \r\nEstrellas del Caribe, Siquito, Sexteto Tabalá, Maria Teresa Villafane, Teto Ocampo, \r\nFrente Cumbiero Transnacional, Son Palenque, Majín Diaz & Kambakuá, \r\nAnne Swing and more.\r\n\r\nCOMING SOON\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="divider-lg">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<div id="outtakes-container-main">\r\n  <ul id="outtakes">\r\n    <li class="outtake">\r\n      <span class="seq">01/</span><span class="seq-total">16</span>\r\n      <div class="outtakes-thumb">&nbsp;</div>\r\n      <b>test</b>\r\n      <div class="btn-rect btn-rect-sm">view more</div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class="outtake">\r\n      <span class="seq">01/</span><span class="seq-total">16</span>\r\n      <div class="outtakes-thumb">&nbsp;</div>\r\n      <b>test</b>\r\n      <div class="btn-rect btn-rect-sm">view more</div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class="outtake">\r\n      <span class="seq">01/</span><span class="seq-total">16</span>\r\n      <div class="outtakes-thumb">&nbsp;</div>\r\n      <b>test</b>\r\n      <div class="btn-rect btn-rect-sm">view more</div>\r\n    </li>\r\n    <li class="outtake">\r\n      <span class="seq">01/</span><span class="seq-total">16</span>\r\n      <div class="outtakes-thumb">&nbsp;</div>\r\n      <b>test</b>\r\n      <div class="btn-rect btn-rect-sm">view more</div>\r\n    </li>\r\n\r\n  </ul>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="divider-lg">&nbsp;</div>\r\n\r\n<br/>\r\n\r\n<div class=